---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Technology | Fluidity Marine">
	<main>
		<section id="tech-hero">
			<h1>Active Boundary Layer <span class="electric-text">Thrust Vectoring</span></h1>
			<p class="tagline">The culmination of digital fluid dynamic control.</p>
		</section>

		<section id="grid">
			<div class="card">
				<h2>ABLTV Core</h2>
				<p>Our proprietary 7-node transom array modulates the boundary layer of the hull, enabling precise yaw control without mechanical rudders.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="card">
				<h2>Differential Drag</h2>
				<p>By modulating the thrust/drag ratio on individual nodes, we achieve better range and precision than traditional mechanical deflection.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="card">
				<h2>Software Defined</h2>
				<p>The system is entirely software-controlled, allowing for millisecond response times and automated station-keeping.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<div class="simulator-link">
			<h3>Want to see it in action?</h3>
			<p>Explore our high-fidelity physics simulator (Desktop Only).</p>
			<a href="/tools/simulator.html" class="button">Launch Simulator &rarr;</a>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 6rem 2rem; }
	h1 { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
	.tagline { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 5rem; }
	
	#grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 6rem; }
	.card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: 24px; }
	.card h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
	.card p { color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; }

	.simulator-link { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%); padding: 4rem; border-radius: 32px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
	.simulator-link h3 { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
	.simulator-link p { margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #94a3b8; }
	
	.button { display: inline-block; padding: 1rem 2rem; background: #00f2fe; color: #050a0f; border-radius: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 800; }
</style>
